version 0.0.2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* FEATURE
    - wrapper around base::rbind() to cope with:
    `lapply( rbind(data.frame(stringsAsFactors=FALSE), "a"), class )`


version 0.0.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* FEATURE
    - 'stringsAsFactors=FALSE'-default wrapper around base::data.frame()
    - 'stringsAsFactors=FALSE'-default wrapper around base::as.data.frame()

